The paper deals with signal detection techniques, which are commonly studied in the fields of information theory (cs.IT) and signal processing (cs.SP). The paper also discusses measures of relative efficiency, which are related to statistical inference and machine learning, making categories such as machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) possible.
